<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>BLESSED ASSURANCE</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ka hechien tai - Lal Isu keia,
 Pathien lopi zie teplawkna ahi;
 Pathien chawk, hukdamna goluoh ding,
 A thagau a pieng thisana sil.

[V2]
 Ziehi ka thusim, ziehi ka la,
 Ka Hukdampa nituma pak hih;
 Ziehi ka thusim, ziehi ka la,
 Ka Hukdampa nituma pak hi.

[V3]
 2. Kipumpiekna leh kipahna kim,
 Nawpna leh kipahna chuh tun ka mui;
 Angelte'n chunglam thu a hun puou,
 Lungsietna leh hehpihna thu chu.

[V4]
 3. Ka puma kipie'n tun ka muong tai,
 Ka Hukdampa ah kipak in ka um;
 Chunglam enin, ka na ngakzing hi,
 A phatna, A hehpihnan ka dim.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>333</hymn_number>
</song>